					TCD Neurovascular exams and 
					cerebral embolic monitoring with transcranial ultrasound can 
					now be performed easily with state of the art digital technology. 
					The <a href="products.html#st3" class="product_link">ST3 Power M-mode Transcranial Doppler</a> is an extremely accurate 
					method of measuring cerebral blood flow velocities and a sensitive method of detecting emboli.
					Spencer’s ST3 TCD systems can be configured to meet your needs whether 
					monitoring stroke patients for <a href="applications.html#vasospasm" class="app_link">vasospasm</a>,
					<a href="applications.html#embolic_monitoring" class="app_link">detecting cerebral emboli</a> or 
					<a href="applications.html#pfo" class="app_link">detecting the presence of a patent foramen ovale (PFO)</a>.</p>
