		<h2 class = "col_sub_heading3">Terumo Trifid Service Status</h2> 
		<hr size="1" width=98% align="center" noshade>
			<p class="col_text3">
			Spencer Technologies will no longer provide service, technical support, or accessories for the Terumo Trifid Transcranial Doppler. The Terumo Trifid model was manufactured exclusively for Terumo Cardiovascular Systems Corporation and production was discontinued in 2007.  If you are still using the Trifid and are interested in upgrading to the Spencer Technologies' current TCD system, please contact <a href="mailto:sales@spencertechnologies.com">sales@spencertechnologies.com</a> for information on our trade-in incentive program.
			</p>			
		
		<h2 class = "col_sub_heading3">Spencer Technologies Has Moved To Redmond Washington</h2> 
